fields.name: Curiosity
fields.about_me: It's been a little lonely up here with Opportunity and Spirit gone... I can't wait for Perseverance to get here so I can help set up its profile!

fields.description: I come here sometimes to collect my thoughts
I wait for trick-or-treaters every year, but no one ever comes :'(
First day on a new planet!
I made it to the Victoria Crater!

fields.author: Kenny
fields.text: These rovers don't move as fast as I thought they would

fields.author: cam
fields.text: I got the high score in Crash Landing!

fields.author: Kenny
fields.text: Curiosity's been working hard for 8 earth years! Happy anniversary!

fields.author: Kenny
fields.text: Hope they get earth accounts added soon
